### **ğŸ“Œ Step 1: Go to Firebase Website**  
1. Open [Firebase](https://firebase.google.com/) â†’ Click **"Get Started"**.  
2. Sign in with your **Google account** (if you donâ€™t have one, create it).  

---

### **ğŸ“Œ Step 2: Create a Firebase Project**  
1. Click **"Create a project"**.  
2. Enter a **Project Name** (e.g., "MyWebsiteDB") â†’ Click **Continue**.  
3. **Disable Google Analytics** (you donâ€™t need it) â†’ Click **Create Project**.  
