### **ğŸ“Œ Step 3: Set Up Firestore Database**  
1. In the Firebase dashboard, click **"Build"** (left menu) â†’ **"Firestore Database"**.  
2. Click **"Create Database"**.  
3. Choose **"Start in test mode"** (so you can add data without restrictions).  
4. Select your **region** (choose the closest to your audience) â†’ Click **Enable**.  
5. Now, your database is ready!  

